Your {c_important}Earthquakes{/c} have a {c_number}[SF_0*100|%|]{/c} chance to spawn a {c_important}Dust Devil{/c} every second that deals {c_number}[SF_1]{/c} damage. {c_important}Earthquake{/c} damage is increased by {c_number}[SF_3*100|%|]{/c} of your Damage vs Close bonus, up to a maximum of {c_number}[SF_4*100|%|]{/c}.

Current Bonus: {c_number}[SF_6 * 100|%x|]{/c}
